      <strong>d20</strong> tables of the small, pleasant occurrences that make a severed-floor
      day feel real. Roll a d20 for any table as needed, or simply pick the entry
      the moment calls for. They are arranged roughly in the order they fit the rhythm
      of a workday.
    </p>
